				\begin{document}$${\beta }_{0}$$\end{document}β0 term and SLDR (Fig. 2 and (a + c) values in Table 1) when AGO1522 cells are exposed to modulated fields, leading to increased radio-resistance of irradiated in-field cells compared to uniformly exposed cells (Fig. 3).

